%h1
  Add credit

%p.lead
  HERE WE SHOULD PLACE INSTRUCTIONS FOR USERS HOW THEY CAN TRANSFER MONEY THROUGH NETELLER
  TO UPTOWNSD WITH LINKS AND SO ON. AND BELOW THERE WILL BE FORM TO NOTIFY UPTOWNSD ABOUT PAYMENT.

= form_for current_user.transactions.build(kind: :deposit),
           html: { class: 'form-horizontal' } do |f|
  = f.hidden_field :user_id
  = f.hidden_field :kind

  %legend
    Confirm your deposit

  .form-group
    = f.label :neteller, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label'
    .col-sm-10
      = f.text_field :neteller, class: 'form-control'

  .form-group
    = f.label :amount, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label'
    .col-sm-10
      = f.number_field :amount, class: 'form-control'

  .form-group
    .col-sm-offset-2.col-sm-10
      = f.submit 'Confirm transfer',
                 class: 'btn btn-primary'

